18:11.077 --> 18:12.883
All right, what's it gonna take?

18:13.162 --> 18:14.008
One...

18:15.090 --> 18:17.993
I want that pit filled in, sir.

18:23.970 --> 18:25.060
Is there a two?

18:25.931 --> 18:28.634
A guaranteed starting spot

18:29.620 --> 18:31.572
on the Indianapolis Colts...

18:32.201 --> 18:33.694
inside linebacker.

18:35.197 --> 18:36.674
We can't accomplish that.

18:36.799 --> 18:39.160
I think that Andy seems like

18:39.285 --> 18:42.519
he doesn't care so much
about the second one.

18:43.108 --> 18:47.112
And he would be fine
with us just filling in the pit.

18:47.693 --> 18:49.255
What do you say, Scott?

18:50.924 --> 18:54.270
- Eventually, we're gonna fill it.
- Eventually?

18:55.722 --> 18:57.753
I've already been
injured in that thing twice.

18:57.878 --> 19:01.096
And I can fall in ten more times
by "eventually".

19:01.535 --> 19:03.781
Every time I walk past that pit,
I'm forced to relive

19:03.906 --> 19:07.853
the most traumatic two separate days
of my life and wanna sue you again.

19:10.846 --> 19:13.069
Well, I hate to say it,

19:13.644 --> 19:16.972
but it really seems like Andy has us
over a barrel here, Scott.

19:20.800 --> 19:22.416
This is really happening.

19:23.247 --> 19:24.621
I can't believe it.

19:26.480 --> 19:29.333
Usually in these situations
a person says "pinch me."

19:32.875 --> 19:34.004
Is that Andy?

19:37.593 --> 19:40.469
Just one of his conditions
for the settlement, I guess.

19:40.594 --> 19:41.644
He settled?

19:43.449 --> 19:46.074
Gave up $100,000 probably.

19:46.199 --> 19:47.536
Just for one thing.

19:48.401 --> 19:50.646
The city fill in the pit
behind your house.

19:51.168 --> 19:51.994
Why?

19:52.607 --> 19:53.666
Who knows?

19:54.497 --> 19:56.819
Who knows why that gopher
does what he does?

19:57.033 --> 19:58.883
You always hated this pit!

20:03.454 --> 20:04.838
Good-bye, pit...

20:05.848 --> 20:07.162
hello, lot.

20:08.124 --> 20:10.374
How does taking risks make me feel?

20:10.936 --> 20:11.936
Amazing.

20:12.945 --> 20:16.127
Tingling sensation
throughout my whole body.

20:16.252 --> 20:17.569
I feel flushed.

20:18.784 --> 20:21.256
My muscles feel relaxed,
yet I feel awake.

20:21.381 --> 20:23.463
Just waves of pleasure.

20:26.189 --> 20:29.251
I wish there was something physical
that can make me feel this way.

20:31.329 --> 20:32.379
You did it.

20:33.120 --> 20:34.848
You thinking what I'm thinking?

20:35.067 --> 20:37.281
- There's so much more to do.
- We're so close!

20:38.477 --> 20:41.259
